Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.22,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,ATOBE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.85,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,AYO, ATOBE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:55.89,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,CATATAN AKTIVITAS PENJELAJAH
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.01,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,BELUM ADA AKTIVITAS YANG TERCATAT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.20,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,GARDA BELAKANG
